title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Fokker F VII Retrofit - managing the engines
description:
In this how to we are going to look how you can manage the engines of the Fokker F VII Retrofit. We will start at the ground with the explanation and some demo's of the usage of the levelers. Once that has been discussed we are going airborn and will show how it works during the flight.
